description:
Many changes:
- Shifted all tracks an eighth note to the left to correct timing
- Updated track names. 
- Made drum track readable
- Cleaned up and corrected vocal track
- Added lyrics (that won't line up in Songsterr but should line up in TuxGuitar)
- Fixed the rhythm of the guitar harmonies in the section between the solos
- Improved both guitar solos using the old tab, the official transcription (which still had errors), and live videos. Not quite perfect, but pretty close.
- Fixed the ending
- Touched up the bass a little bit, but it could still use some work. I don't think there's so many open strings and some of the fills are incomplete/missing.
title: Die With Your Boots On
